Label: Title of Dataset
Value: Nigeria - Subnational Demographic and Health Data

Label: Description
Value: Contains data from the DHS data portal. There is also a dataset containing Nigeria - National Demographic and Health Data on HDX. The DHS Program Application Programming Interface (API) provides software developers access to aggregated indicator data from The Demographic and Health Surveys (DHS) Program. The API can be used to create various applications to help analyze, visualize, explore and disseminate data on population, health, HIV, and nutrition from more than 90 countries.
